Package: landlord
Title: Decide whether a rental property investment is profitable
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Rudy', 'Pastel', email = 'rudy.pastel@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: For an investor, a property and a loan, the landlord package calculates
  future cash flows and profitability. For convenience sake, this can be done
  via a Shiny dashboard too.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
